opam-version: "2.0"
version: "0.0.1"
synopsis: "Unofficial Weights & Biases SDK for OCaml"
description:
  "wandb-ocaml is an unofficial OCaml SDK for Weights & Biases, a platform for experiment tracking, dataset versioning, and model management. The SDK provides a simple and intuitive API for logging metrics, hyperparameters, and artifacts to Weights & Biases during the training process of machine learning models."
